          <li><strong>Monthly deep tasks:</strong> Rotate through one room per month for detailed attention</li>
          <li><strong>Seasonal check-ins:</strong> Brief cleaning sessions at each season change</li>
          <li><strong>Consider recurring service:</strong> Many Nashville families find that biweekly professional cleaning maintains the spring clean results</li>
        </ul>

